  "title": "Landscape Supervisor",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Ensure work tasks are completed on time.</li>\n  <li>Handle client questions on the landscape project.</li>\n  <li>Identify symptoms, pests and diseases.</li>\n  <li>Improve growing conditions using proper nutrient fertilisers and soil mix.</li>\n  <li>Manage landscape maintenance works (Pruning, Weeding, Mulching)</li>\n  <li>Organise work orders with the ground crew.</li>\n  <li>Esnure and plan work safety regulations are followed.</li>\n  <li>Plan daily work schedule for the workforce.</li>\n  <li>Review of the plant health, soil, water and other environmental conditions.</li>\n  <li>Review sites according to the health and safety regulations.</li>\n</ul>",
